<section class="intro-section">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="section-header">
      <h2 class="section-title">¿Quiénes somos?</h2>
      <div class="title-divider">
        <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="40" height="40" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="icon-chemistry">
          <path d="M9 2v6l-3 3.5c-.5.5-.5 1.5 0 2l3 3.5v6"></path>
          <path d="M15 2v6l3 3.5c.5.5.5 1.5 0 2l-3 3.5v6"></path>
          <circle cx="12" cy="12" r="2"></circle>
        </svg>
        <div class="divider-line"></div>
        <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="32" height="32" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="icon-mining">
          <path d="M3 12h18m-9-9v18"></path>
          <circle cx="12" cy="12" r="3"></circle>
          <path d="M8 8l8 8m0-8l-8 8"></path>
        </svg>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="intro-card">
      <div class="intro-icon">
        <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="64" height="64" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="feather feather-award">
          <circle cx="12" cy="8" r="7"></circle>
          <polyline points="8.21 13.89 7 22 12 17 17 22 15.79 13.88"></polyline>
        </svg>
      </div>
      <div class="intro-content">
        <p class="intro-text">
          En <strong>IMEXSE SRL</strong>, contamos con un área de productos químicos enfocados al sector minero. Nos enorgullece haber logrado a lo largo de <span class="highlight">30 años</span> una amplia experiencia en la minería aurífera, detectando un gran potencial para los proyectos mineros, por lo que en esta área importamos químicos de alta calidad.
        </p>
        <a href="/nosotros" class="cta-button-intro">Conoce más</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .intro-section {
    padding: 6rem 0;
    background: linear-gradient(180deg, #f8fafc 0%, #f1f5f9 100%);
    margin-top: 0; /* Ajustado para el nuevo diseño sin solapamiento */
    position: relative;
    z-index: 1;
  }

  .container {
    max-width: 1100px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 0 2rem;
  }

  .section-header {
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
    opacity: 0;
    transform: translateY(30px);
    animation: fadeInUp 1s 0.2s ease-out forwards;
  }

  .section-title {
    font-size: 2rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: #0B1F38;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    font-family: 'Montserrat', sans-serif;
    letter-spacing: -0.5px;
  }

  .title-divider {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    gap: 1rem;
    margin-bottom: 0;
  }

  .divider-line {
    width: 60px;
    height: 2px;
    background: #0E6FA3;
    border-radius: 1px;
  }

  .icon-chemistry,
  .icon-mining {
    color: #0E6FA3;
    opacity: 0.8;
    transition: all 0.3s ease;
  }

  .icon-chemistry:hover,
  .icon-mining:hover {
    color: #FF6B00;
    transform: scale(1.1);
  }

  .intro-card {
    background: var(--color-white);
    border-radius: 1.5rem;
    padding: 4rem;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 3rem;
    box-shadow: 0 25px 50px -12px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.08);
    border: 1px solid rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05);
    opacity: 0;
    transform: translateY(40px);
    animation: fadeInUp 1.2s 0.5s ease-out forwards;
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .intro-card::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    top: 0;
    left: 0;
    right: 0;
    height: 4px;
    background: linear-gradient(90deg, #0E6FA3 0%, #FF6B00 100%);
    opacity: 0.8;
  }

  @keyframes fadeInUp {
    to {
      opacity: 1;
      transform: translateY(0);
    }
  }

  .intro-icon {
    flex-shrink: 0;
    width: 100px;
    height: 100px;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--color-blue-light), var(--color-blue));
    border-radius: 50%;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    color: var(--color-white);
    box-shadow: 0 10px 20px rgba(3, 105, 161, 0.2);
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .intro-icon::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    top: -50%;
    left: -50%;
    width: 200%;
    height: 200%;
    background: linear-gradient(45deg, transparent, rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1), transparent);
    transform: rotate(45deg);
    animation: shimmer 3s ease-in-out infinite;
  }

  @keyframes shimmer {
    0%, 100% { transform: translateX(-100%) translateY(-100%) rotate(45deg); }
    50% { transform: translateX(100%) translateY(100%) rotate(45deg); }
  }
  
  .intro-icon svg {
      width: 50px;
      height: 50px;
      z-index: 1;
      position: relative;
  }

  .intro-content {
    text-align: left;
  }

  .intro-text {
    font-size: 1.15rem;
    line-height: 1.8;
    color: var(--color-text);
    font-weight: 400;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }

  .intro-text strong {
    color: var(--color-navy);
    font-weight: 600;
  }
  
  .intro-text .highlight {
    color: var(--color-orange);
    font-weight: 700;
    font-size: 1.2rem;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #fef3c7, #fed7aa);
    padding: 0.2rem 0.6rem;
    border-radius: 8px;
    position: relative;
    white-space: nowrap;
  }

  .cta-button-intro {
    display: inline-block;
    background: var(--color-blue);
    color: var(--color-white);
    padding: 0.9rem 1.8rem;
    border-radius: 50px;
    font-weight: 600;
    font-size: 1rem;
    text-decoration: none;
    transition: all 0.3s ease;
    box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(3, 105, 161, 0.2);
  }

  .cta-button-intro:hover {
    background: var(--color-blue-dark);
    transform: translateY(-3px);
    box-shadow: 0 6px 20px rgba(3, 105, 161, 0.3);
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .intro-section {
      padding: 4rem 1rem;
    }
    
    .section-title {
      font-size: 2.2rem;
    }
    
    .title-divider {
      gap: 0.75rem;
    }
    
    .divider-line {
      width: 40px;
    }
    
    .icon-chemistry,
    .icon-mining {
      width: 28px;
      height: 28px;
    }
    
    .intro-card {
      flex-direction: column;
      padding: 3rem 2rem;
      text-align: center;
      gap: 2rem;
    }
    
    .intro-content {
      text-align: center;
    }
    
    .intro-text {
      font-size: 1.05rem;
    }

    .cta-button-intro {
      padding: 0.8rem 1.5rem;
      font-size: 0.95rem;
    }
  }
</style>
